com.djzass.medipoint.logic_database

Class DbContract

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.djzass.medipoint.logic_database.DbContract

  • public class DbContract
extends java.lang.Object
    This is container for constants that define names for URIs, tables, and columns and made global hence available across all the other classes within the same package. The inner class for each table is then created to enumerates its columns. There are seven tables in total, they are:
    1. AccountEntry
    2. AppointmentEntry
    3. ClinicEntry
    4. SpecialtyEntry
    5. DoctorEntry
    6. DoctorScheduleEntry
    7. ServiceEntry
    8. PatientEntry
    Since:
    2015
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Deka
    See Also:
    BaseColumns
